AddressInfo.Title: Enfinity
AddressInfo.AccessComments: Route  Take the exit 'WAREGEM' on the E17 · Follow the direction of Waregem and at the lights, go straight ahead · At the roundabout (with sportshop Del Sport on your right hand side) go straight ahead ·  You'll reach another set of traffic lights, keep going straight ahead · at the following lights you turn left at the direction of 'DEERLIJK & VICHTE' · You've reached the Henri Lebbestraat, Enfinity office is about 300 meters on your right.
